          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "算来总是朕的错，"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "决不该用了贼王忠。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "堪堪攻破彰仪门。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "他通了闯贼将城献"
        },
        {
          "character": "周后",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "既然贼人将城临，"
        },
        {
          "character": "周后",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "臣妾焉敢去逃生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周后",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "顾不得金枝玉叶人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周后",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "二十四拜辞主公。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周后",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我今舍了娇生两个子"
        },
        {
          "character": "周后",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "低下头来忙跪倒"
        },
        {
          "character": "周后",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "我抽身就往御园走"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "梓橦，你要怎么样？"
        },
        {
          "character": "周后",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "御果园内去丧生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "太子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "皇娘，难道舍了孩儿不成？"
        },
        {
          "character": "周后",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孩儿呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周后",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "倘然闯贼将宫进，"
        },
        {
          "character": "周后",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你皇娘千载落丑名。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周后",
          "line_type": "哭",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孩儿呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "周后",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "可怜你兄妹两个人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "周后",
          "line_type": "西皮流水板",
          "musical_style": "西皮流水板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "要相逢除非一梦中。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（周后下。崇祯哭。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "眼看梓橦投井死，"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，梓橦呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "却把为王摘了心。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（内监上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "内监",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你快把太子领出宫。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "改名换姓去逃生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不由我满眼落泪痕。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "反不如民间作穷人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "手向腰间拔青铜。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你领着逃出京城外"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "回头来看娇生女"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你虽是生长昭阳院"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为父的出于无可奈"
        },
        {
          "character": "公主",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，父王呀，难道杀了孩儿么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为父的出于无可奈，"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "望着姣生下绝情。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（公主下。报子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万岁爷，不好了，贼把彰仪门打开。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "王承恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启我主，贼把彰仪门打开，我主快快换衣服，溜出城门，再作商量。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今大事已去，你叫朕往哪里逃走去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "满京城尽都是贼的人马，"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "却叫孤家哪里行？"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "不肯丧在贼手中。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "为王前到万寿亭。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "四面八方烟尘起，"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "火炮不住响连声。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "他说过事到紧急看分明。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王承恩，把铁冠道人昔日进的画图取来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我宁可死在昭阳院"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王承恩前面引着路"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忽想起铁冠道人留图画"
        },
        {
          "character": "王承恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴婢取来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王承恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万岁，画图在此。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "展开呀。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为王一见痴呆了，"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不由我顶上走真魂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "脖子排了一条绳。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他数年以来算得清。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为王焉能逆天行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为王误了天下民。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可惜我多少保国臣。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王承恩，你把以前边上报来，阵中亡身，骂贼殉难，这些死节的忠臣图挂起。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我看他蓬头跣足发盖面"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这分明是王真形象"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢罢罢，原来天数安排定"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这就是无能臣子误了朕"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我明家大数虽然尽"
        },
        {
          "character": "王承恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴婢晓得。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "王承恩。"
        },
        {
          "character": "王承恩",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "奴婢在。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "若是朝中大臣，亡身为国，得似这些武将，焉有今日！"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "为王一见痛伤情，"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "两眼不住落泪痕。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "万古千秋落好名。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "昌平州好一个李子修；"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "夜裸贼营孙传廷；"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "陕西城又死了赵昔云；"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "宣府里杀了朱之文；"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可怜那福州洪苏云；"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "雪夜里前去刨贼坟；"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可怜他乱箭丧了身；"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一家团团用火焚；"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "赤胆忠心只有这王承恩。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有几个阵上丧了生；"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有几个连营分了身；"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有几个满城老幼送了生。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "霎时间震得天地昏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你且引朕向前行。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "煤山以上看分明。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "贼子此地将人砍，"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大炮连天把屋焚。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咳，皇天呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我舍了祖宗创来的花世界，"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我舍了十六帝的众皇陵；"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我舍了忠君保国众能臣；"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我舍了安分守己好良民。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咬破了玉指血淋淋。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你须要按字行行看分明："
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "造罪原是朕一人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "千万莫害众黎民。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "十七年寸草不收成。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "扰得他东奔西逃不安宁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "田产家园去个清。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "天地鬼神也不容。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "可怜为王自伤情。"
        },
        {
          "character": "崇祯",
          "line_type": "唱",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "煤山上缢死我崇祯。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（崇祯下。王承恩下。）"
        }
